@using Conversey.BL.Administration
@using Conversey.UI_MVC.Models
@using Conversey.UI_MVC.Resources
@inject AdminContext AdminContext
@inject IAdminI18nService I18n
@inject IWorkspaceManager WorkspaceManager

@{
    var workspaces = WorkspaceManager.GetAllWorkspaces();
}

<aside class="hidden lg:flex fixed inset-y-0 left-0 w-[17rem] flex-col border-r border-secondary/10 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur z-40">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 border-t border-secondary/10" style="top: var(--admin-header-height, 4rem);"></div>
    <div class="px-4 py-3">
        <a asp-controller="AdminProfile" asp-action="Index" class="group flex items-center gap-3 px-2 py-0 text-text hover:text-primary transition-colors">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-secondary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
                </svg>
            </span>
            <div class="min-w-0">
                <div class="text-xs font-bold truncate">@AdminContext.CurrentAdmin.Email</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-secondary">@I18n["Conversey Admin"]</div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>

    <nav class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-4 py-5 space-y-2" data-sidebar-nav>
        @* ── Dashboard ── *@
        <a href="/admin" class="sidebar-link flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold text-text/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all shrink-0" data-sidebar-page="/admin">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-background border border-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7m-9 2v8m4-8v8m5-13l2 2"></path></svg>
            </span>
            Dashboard
        </a>

        @* ── Workspaces (expandable) ── *@
        <div class="sidebar-section" data-sidebar-section>
            <button type="button" class="sidebar-section-toggle flex items-center gap-3 w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold text-text/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all" data-sidebar-toggle="workspaces" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-background border border-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h10"></path></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="flex-1 text-left">Workspaces</span>
                <svg class="sidebar-chevron w-3.5 h-3.5 text-secondary shrink-0 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="sidebar-section-content hidden ml-5 mt-1 space-y-0.5" data-sidebar-content="workspaces">
                <a href="/admin/workspaces" class="sidebar-link sidebar-sublink flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-text/50 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all" data-sidebar-page="/admin/workspaces">
                    <span class="w-3 h-3 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">+</span>
                    View all
                </a>
                @foreach (var ws in workspaces)
                {
                    <a href="/admin/workspaces/@ws.Id" class="sidebar-link sidebar-sublink flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium text-text/50 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all truncate" data-sidebar-page="/admin/workspaces/@ws.Id" title="@ws.Name">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 shrink-0 text-primary/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                        @ws.Name
                    </a>
                }
            </div>
        </div>

        @* ── AI Dashboard ── *@
        <a href="/admin/ai" class="sidebar-link flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold text-text/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all shrink-0" data-sidebar-page="/admin/ai">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-background border border-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            AI Dashboard
        </a>

        @* ── Analytics ── *@
        <a href="/admin/conversey/analytics" class="sidebar-link flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold text-text/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all shrink-0" data-sidebar-page="/admin/conversey/analytics">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-background border border-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            Analytics
        </a>

        @* ── Admins ── *@
        <a href="/admin/conversey/admins" class="sidebar-link flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold text-text/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all shrink-0" data-sidebar-page="/admin/conversey/admins">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-background border border-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/></svg>
            </span>
            Admins
        </a>
    </nav>

    <div class="mt-auto px-4 py-5">
        <form class="w-full" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Page("/Account/Login", new { area = "Identity" })" method="post">
            <button type="submit" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-accent/30 text-accent font-bold text-sm hover:bg-accent/5 transition-all">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 16l4-4m0 0l-4-4m4 4H7m6 4v1a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v1"></path></svg>
                Log out
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</aside>

<script>
(function() {
    var currentPath = window.location.pathname;

    function highlightLink(link) {
        var page = link.getAttribute('data-sidebar-page');
        if (page && currentPath.startsWith(page)) {
            link.classList.remove('text-text/70', 'text-text/50');
            link.classList.add('text-primary', 'bg-primary/5');
            return true;
        }
        return false;
    }

    document.querySelectorAll('[data-sidebar-page]').forEach(function(link) {
        highlightLink(link);
    });

    var LS_KEY = 'conversey_sidebar_sections';

    function loadState() {
        try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_KEY) || '{}'); } catch(e) { return {}; }
    }

    function saveState(state) {
        try { localStorage.setItem(LS_KEY, JSON.stringify(state)); } catch(e) {}
    }

    var state = loadState();

    document.querySelectorAll('[data-sidebar-toggle]').forEach(function(toggle) {
        var section = toggle.getAttribute('data-sidebar-toggle');
        var content = document.querySelector('[data-sidebar-content="' + section + '"]');
        var chevron = toggle.querySelector('.sidebar-chevron');
        if (!content) return;

        function setOpen(open) {
            toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', open ? 'true' : 'false');
            if (open) {
                content.classList.remove('hidden');
                if (chevron) chevron.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
            } else {
                content.classList.add('hidden');
                if (chevron) chevron.style.transform = '';
            }
            state[section] = open;
            saveState(state);
        }

        var hasActiveChild = content.querySelectorAll('[data-sidebar-page]').length > 0 &&
            Array.from(content.querySelectorAll('[data-sidebar-page]')).some(function(link) {
                return currentPath.startsWith(link.getAttribute('data-sidebar-page') || '');
            });

        var stored = state[section];
        var shouldOpen = hasActiveChild || stored === true;

        if (shouldOpen) setOpen(true);

        toggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
            var isOpen = toggle.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
            setOpen(!isOpen);
        });
    });
})();
</script>
